{"tid":981043,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"進口慘錄負增長 12月中國進出口遠遜預期","createTime":"2019-01-14T03:24:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-14T04:57:46.000Z","uid":50386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9fe7280ff86f923861c42923be4b193fa9dfd509","tid":981043,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T03:24:59.000Z","msg":"中國公佈12月及全年進出口總值，其中12月進出口數據均遠遜預期，出口更錄負增長。以人民幣計算，12月進口總值11,399億元人民幣，按年下跌3.1%，較上月跌9.7%，遠遜預期的增長12%；出口總值15,349億元人民幣，按年微升0.2%，較上月跌0.9%，亦低於預期的6.6%。"},{"pid":"828eff2a50a294dbe67d7e434585e0e601b25eb5","tid":981043,"uid":101945,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T03:28:06.000Z","msg":"下降 都講成增長加個負<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41ac8e7232f3af57450c3301cb246066c91b1954","tid":981043,"uid":177211,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T04:52:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f9b12df1c937008df57b43a676d9ff2b7a7f9893","tid":981043,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T04:57:46.000Z","msg":"-3.1  vs  12%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}